{
  "stem": "23090.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the shoes were made of-- the Holland shoes, they were wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was nails around those, and those nails would sometimes just come loose or something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And your feet, it just-- you just could not survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It just-- that's why I'm looking today, I says, how did-- how did I survive?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And some of these other people?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, I know not everybody experienced my experience, and I didn't experience a lot of things that-- the horrible things that happened to other people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when you march under these conditions, and you stay in forests under these conditions, and you are under-- under-- you know, if you go out right now, half-naked in this weather right now, you stay out there for two, or three, or four hours, and not come in with some sort of a pneumonia or some sickness, it would be a very lucky experience for you.",
      "word_count": 67
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It would be a miracle that you don't get sick.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I say to you, I don't know how we survived that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Forget about the hunger, I'm talking about the natural elements.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The very thing that kills people, is a miracle on its own.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so when I go into April with you, you know, I'm going from September, and I go through the four weeks here, and the six weeks there, I'm not saying this in a very light way.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm saying that these were the hardest times, not just by being brutalized and being-- being under the-- under the conditions of being a kid in a concentration camp, but the elements, the elements were as horrendous as the whole concept of the concentration camps were.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So getting into April was a miracle by itself.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
